 the Scots?</h3></a><p>In 2012, an American single malt whiskey from Balcones Distillery in Texas defeated nine other world-class single malts from around the world and gained international attention. Today, the American version of Scotch is still booming, reinforced by a number of new distilleries.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/01/02/best-scotches-under-100-dollars/">The Competitor, Scotch</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/new-orleans-travel-guide/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/72-new-orleans-gear-patrol-lead-650-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">Laissez les bon temps rouler</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/new-orleans-travel-guide/"><h3>72 Hours in New Orleans</h3></a><p>Where to stay, what to eat and what to do with 72 hours in New Orleans.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/category/travel-and-adventure/">Travel &amp; Adventure</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/alpine-world-ski-championships-photo-essay/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/FIS-BC-Gear-Patrol-LEAD-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">Step Down, Lindsey Vonn</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/alpine-world-ski-championships-photo-essay/"><h3>On the Slopes for the Alpine World Ski Championships</h3></a><p>The Alpine World Ski Championships, held in Beaver Creek, CO, featured the best skiers in the world. And Tiger Woods.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/tag/skiing/">More Alpine Skiing</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/complications-the-chronograph/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Chronograph-video-gear-patrol-LEad-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">It's Complicated, Vol. 1</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/complications-the-chronograph/"><h3>The Chronograph, Explained</h3></a><p>While most of us won’t time anything beyond a boring meeting or boiling eggs, a chronograph is all about readiness, potential and the human interaction with a micro-engineering marvel -- not to mention the rare opportunity to stop time.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2014/12/29/best-2014-timekeeping/">The Best of Timekeeping 2014</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/photo-essay-french-quarter/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/photo-essay-gear-patrol-lead650-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">NOLA's French Quarter</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/photo-essay-french-quarter/"><h3>Admiring a Small Part of the Big Easy</h3></a><p>Locals simply call it "The Quarter", in their Brooklyn-esque yat. It's a clipping of convenience, and unwittingly accurate.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/category/photo-essay/">Travel Photography</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/best-waterproof-boots-for-men/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/essentials-waterproof-gear-patrol-lead-650-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">Keep Your Dogs Safe and Warm</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/best-waterproof-boots-for-men/"><h3>The Best Waterproof Boots f