i” Lengyel realize their ultimate vision, that’s just the beginning. </p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2014/10/23/25-best-restaurants-in-america/">25 Best Restaurants in America</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/today-gear-february-13-2015/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/m-pear-pocket-square-lead-650-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">What's New, Now</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/13/today-gear-february-13-2015/"><h3>Today in Gear: February 13, 2015</h3></a><p>Ready for the weekend with Quoddy and Leffot's Christopher Street Collection, <em>Evolve</em> for the PS4, Jim Beam's Bottled-in-Bond Bourbon and more.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://www.gearpatrol.com/category/today-in-gear/">Gear News</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/12/winter-camping-on-the-appalachian-trail/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/WinterCamping-GearPatrol-LEAD-320x246.jpg" width="320" height="246" /></a></div><div class="body-wrap"><div class="intro">The Warmth of Frozen Land</div><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/12/winter-camping-on-the-appalachian-trail/"><h3>Winter Camping, A Video Buying Guide</h3></a><p>We hiked and camped along the Appalachian Trail on a very chilly and windy weekend and had a damn good time.</p><div class="fadeout"></div></div><div class="more">More: <a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/01/16/winter-camping-essential-gear/" title="15 Winter Camping Essentials">15 Winter Camping Essentials</a></div></article><article><div class="img-wrap"><a href="http://gearpatrol.com/2015/02/12/spire-review/"><img class="gp-ll" data-original="http://gearpatrol.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Spire-Tes